# DES Y5 Supernovae
### Likelihood for MontePython 

14 November 2025: 

Tanvi Karwal hacking together a version of the DES Y5 Supernova likelihood
bsed on the DESY5 supernova Dovekie likelihood with files available at 
https://github.com/des-science/DES-SN5YR/tree/main/4_DISTANCES_COVMAT

## Instructions 

1) Copy the DESY5 data to the data/ folder in MP from https://github.com/des-science/DES-SN5YR/tree/main/4_DISTANCES_COVMAT
2) Copy the covmat into the same folder https://github.com/des-science/DES-SN5YR/blob/main/4_DISTANCES_COVMAT/STAT%2BSYS.npz
3) No nuisance parameters. Call by adding to your MP experiment block:
```
data.experiments=['DESY5_SNe']
```
